{"word":"Sanctification","slug":"sanctification","sections":[{"paragraph":""},{"paragraph":""},{"paragraph":"<b>Sanctification</b> Firstborn of Israelites sanctified<br/> <a href='https://www.wordofgod.in/bibles/?book=2&chapter=13&verse=2'>Exo 13:2</a><br/> All Israel sanctified<br/> <a href='https://www.wordofgod.in/bibles/?book=2&chapter=19&verse=10'>Exo 19:10</a>; <a href='https://www.wordofgod.in/bibles/?book=2&chapter=19&verse=14'>Exo 19:14</a><br/> Material things sanctified by anointing<br/> <a href='https://www.wordofgod.in/bibles/?book=2&chapter=40&verse=11'>Exo 40:11</a><br/> The Lord, the sanctifier<br/> <a href='https://www.wordofgod.in/bibles/?book=2&chapter=31&verse=13'>Exo 31:13</a>; <a href='https://www.wordofgod.in/bibles/?book=3&chapter=20&verse=8'>Lev 20:8</a>; <a href='https://www.wordofgod.in/bibles/?book=3&chapter=21&verse=8'>Lev 21:8</a>; <a href='https://www.wordofgod.in/bibles/?book=3&chapter=22&verse=9'>Lev 22:9</a><br/> The altar sanctifies the gift<br/> <a href='https://www.wordofgod.in/bibles/?book=2&chapter=29&verse=37'>Exo 29:37</a>; <a href='https://www.wordofgod.in/bibles/?book=2&chapter=30&verse=29'>Exo 30:29</a><br/> Tabernacle sanctified by God's presence<br/> <a href='https://www.wordofgod.in/bibles/?book=2&chapter=29&verse=43'>Exo 29:43</a>; <a href='https://www.wordofgod.in/bibles/?book=2&chapter=40&verse=35'>Exo 40:35</a><br/> Unclassified scriptures relating to<br/> <a href='https://www.wordofgod.in/bibles/?book=2&chapter=31&verse=13'>Exo 31:13</a>; <a href='https://www.wordofgod.in/bibles/?book=2&chapter=33&verse=16'>Exo 33:16</a>; <a href='https://www.wordofgod.in/bibles/?book=3&chapter=21&verse=23'>Lev 21:23</a>; <a href='https://www.wordofgod.in/bibles/?book=24&chapter=1&verse=5'>Jer 1:5</a>; <a href='https://www.wordofgod.in/bibles/?book=26&chapter=37&verse=28'>Eze 37:28</a>; <a href='https://www.wordofgod.in/bibles/?book=43&chapter=17&verse=17'>Joh 17:17</a>; <a href='https://www.wordofgod.in/bibles/?book=43&chapter=17&